<!--// 저자의 다른책 -->
<div class="writerBoxWrap2">
<div class="writerInfo">
<div class="infoTitle">
<span class="writerName">이준영 [저]</span>
<a class="btnPopOver bt_newSMSreg" href="#" id="newBsms" onclick="fn_smsAuthor('1000055065', '이준영');return false;">신작알림 SMS신청</a>
<a class="bt_writerDB" href="#" onclick='fn_wiseLogRedirect("bottom","Author","bookdb","http://bookdb.co.kr/bdb/PersonDictionary.do?_method=writerDetail&amp;writerCategoryNo=1&amp;sc.page=1&amp;prsnNo=1000055065","_blank");return false;'>작가DB보기</a>
</div>
<div class="infoContent">
<div class="infoC_left">
<table class="tb_infoC">
<colgroup>
<col style="width:80px;"/>
<col style="width:100px;"/>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th>생년월일</th>
<td>-</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="infoC_right">
<p class="infoC_cont">
저자 이준영은 상명대학교 소비자주거학과 조교수로 재직하고 있다. 서울대학교 생활과학대학 소비자학과에서 학사·석사·박사학위를 받았다. 2012년 한국소비자정책교육학회 최우수논문상, 2011년 한국소비자학회 우수논문상 등을 수상했다. 2014년에는 경상북도 도지사 표창을 받았다. 서울대학교 소비트렌드분석센터(CTC), LG전자 LSR(Life Soft Research)연구소에서 근무했다. 현재 상명대학교 소비자분석연구소 소장을 맡고 있다. 주요 관심 분야는 소비트렌드, 소비자 행태, 소비자 유통(retailing)이다.
                                        </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    function handle_naver_ads_response(response) {
        var htmlStr="";
        if (response.ads.length  > 0) {
	        for(var i=0, len = (response.ads.length > 3?3:response.ads.length); i < len; i++){
	        		 htmlStr += '<li>';
	                 htmlStr += '   <a href=\''+response.ads[i].clickUrl+'\' target=\'_blank\'>';
	                 htmlStr += '       <span class="number">'+(i+1)+'</span>';
	                 htmlStr += '       <span class="text">';
	                 htmlStr += '           <span class="underline">'+response.ads[i].headline+'</span> - '+response.ads[i].description;
	                 htmlStr += '       </span>';
	                 htmlStr += '       <span class="url">'+response.ads[i].displayUrl+'</span>';
	                 htmlStr += '   </a>';
	                 htmlStr += '</li>';
	        }
            
            document.getElementById("naverPowerLink").style.display = 'block';
            document.getElementById("powerLinkArea").innerHTML = htmlStr;
        }
    }
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
/*---------------- 마우스 click XY --------------------*/
$(document).ready(function(){
    $(".btnLink").click(function(event){
        var item = $(this).attr("id");
        var popItem = "popClick_" + item;
        var parentOffset = $(this).parent().offset();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var mouseX = event.pageX;
        var mouseY = event.pageY;

        var browserWidth = document.body.clientWidth;
        var browserHeight = $(window).height();
        var parentWrap = $('div#gateCon');
        var totalWidth = parentWrap;
        var rightWidth = $("#" + popItem).innerWidth();
        var rightHeight = $("#" + popItem).innerHeight();
        var couponTop = ($(this).offset().top) + $(this).height(); // 할인쿠폰 레이어 top 위치
        var offsetWidth = document.body.offsetWidth;
        var $incAll_wrap = $('.incAll_wrap').width();
        var couponRight = ((offsetWidth - $incAll_wrap) / 2) + 2;

        $(".ly_popDarkGray").css("display", "none");
        $(".ly_popupAllBox").css("display", "");

        if (popItem === 'popClick_lyCPop4') { //할인쿠폰 레이어일 경우
            $("#" + popItem).css({
                "display" : "block",
                "top" : couponTop,
                "right" : couponRight
            });

            // 할인쿠폰 레이어 리사이징 on
            $(window).on('resize.discountPopupLayer', function() {
                var resizeOffsetWidth = document.body.offsetWidth;
                var resizeCouponRight = ((resizeOffsetWidth - $incAll_wrap) / 2) + 2;

                if (resizeOffsetWidth <= $incAll_wrap) {
                    $("#" + popItem).css ({
                        "right" : 2
                    });
                } else {
                    $("#" + popItem).css({
                        "right" : resizeCouponRight
                    });
                }
            });
        } else {
            if(browserWidth > totalWidth){
                if(mouseX + rightWidth > browserWidth){
                  mouseX = browserWidth - rightWidth - ((browserWidth - totalWidth) / 2) - 5;
                }else{
                  mouseX = mouseX - ((browserWidth - totalWidth) / 2);
                }
            }else{
                if(mouseX + rightWidth > browserWidth){
                  mouseX = browserWidth - rightWidth - 5;
                }
            }
            $("#" + popItem).css({
                "display" : "block",
                "left" : mouseX,
                "top" : mouseY + 10
            });
        }
    });

    /* 20160212 - 추가 */
    $(".btnPopOver").mouseenter(function(event){
        var item = $(this).attr("id");
        var popItem = "popOver_" + item;
        var parentOffset = $(this).parent().offset();
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var mouseX = event.pageX;
        var mouseY = event.pageY;

        var browserWidth = document.body.clientWidth;
        var browserHeight = $(window).height();
        var parentWrap = $('div.incAll_wrap');
        var totalWidth = parentWrap.innerWidth();
        var rightWidth = $("#" + popItem).innerWidth();
        var rightHeight = $("#" + popItem).innerHeight();

        if(browserWidth > totalWidth){
            if(mouseX + rightWidth > browserWidth){
                mouseX = browserWidth - rightWidth - 5;
            }
        }else{
            if(mouseX + rightWidth > browserWidth){
                mouseX = browserWidth - rightWidth - 5;
            }
        }
        $("#" + popItem).css({
            "display" : "block",
            "left" : mouseX,
            "top" : mouseY-5
        });
    });
    $(".btnPopOver").mouseleave(function(){
        var item = $(this).attr("id");
        var popItem = "popOver_" + item;
        $("#" + popItem).css("display", "none");
    });
    /* //20160212 - 추가 */
});

$(function(){
    var $tabWraper = $('.contentTabWrap');
    var $contentTab =  $tabWraper.find('a');
    var $contentWrap = $('.contentsWrap');
    var tabHeight = $('.contentTabWrap').height();
    var onTabIdx = 0;
    var moveTime = 300;
    var tabMove = function(){
        var winScrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        var contentHeight = $('#inc_contentWrap').height();
        var contentOffsetTop = $('#inc_contentWrap').offset().top;
        if(winScrollTop < contentOffsetTop){
            $tabWraper.removeClass('fixed1');
        } else {
            if(winScrollTop > contentHeight + contentOffsetTop){
                $tabWraper.animate({top: -1 * tabHeight }, moveTime);
            } else {
                $tabWraper.addClass('fixed1').removeAttr('style');
            }
        }
        $contentTab.each(function(index){
            var tabTotalTop = $contentWrap.eq(index).offset().top + $contentWrap.eq(index).height();
            if(winScrollTop < tabTotalTop - tabHeight ){
                onTabIdx = index;
                return false;
            }
        });
        $contentTab.parent('li').removeClass('selected');
        $contentTab.eq(onTabIdx).parent('li').addClass('selected');
    };
    $(window).on('load scroll', tabMove);
    $contentTab.on('click', function(e){
        var $target = $(this.hash);
        var targetOffset = $target.offset().top;
        $('html,body').stop().animate({scrollTop: targetOffset - tabHeight + 10}, moveTime);
        e.preventDefault();
    });
});

$(function(){
    var stickyNavTop = $('#bookCart_Type1_miniBar').offset().top;
    var stickyNav = function(){
        var scrollTop = $(window).scrollTop();
        if(scrollTop > stickyNavTop) {
            $('.nav').addClass('sticky').stop().animate({top:0}, 500)
        } else {
            $('.nav').addClass('sticky').stop().animate({top:-60}, 500)
        }
    };
    stickyNav();
    $(window).scroll(function() {
        stickyNav();
    });
});
</script>
<!-- GA 태깅 -->
<script type="text/javascript">
    var gaCategory = '도서' + '^' + getStdClsNm(1) + '^' + getStdClsNm(2) + '^' + getStdClsNm(3) + '^' + getStdClsNm(4); //상품옵션 : 옵션1^옵션2^옵션3 (띄어쓰기없음)(데이터 없을경우 공백)(중간에 ^ 주의) 
	
    function getStdClsNm(depth) {
        var stdClsNm = "Book > 경제경영 > 경제 > 경제전망";
        if(stdClsNm == '' || typeof stdClsNm == 'undefined') {
            return '';
        } else {
            stdClsNm = stdClsNm.split('>');
            for(var i=0 ; i<stdClsNm.length ; i++) {
                stdClsNm[i] = stdClsNm[i].trim();
            }
            if(depth <= stdClsNm.length) {
                return stdClsNm[depth-1];
            } else {
                return '';
            }
        }
    }
    
    function getPrdList(arguments, gaPrdInfo) {
        var prdTp = '';
        var prdList = [];
        
        if(arguments.length != 0) {
            prdTp = arguments[0];
        }
        
        if(prdTp == 'ebook') {
            gaCategory = '도서' + '^' + prdTp + '^' + getStdClsNm(2);            
            gaPrdInfo.id = arguments[1];
            gaPrdInfo.price = $('#EB_DISP_SALE_UNITCOST' + gaPrdInfo.id ).val();
            prdList[0] = gaPrdInfo;
        } else if(prdTp == 'fancy') {
            prdList = arguments[1];
        } else {
        	prdList[0] = gaPrdInfo;
        }
        
        return prdList;
    }
    
    function getPrdListToJson(prdList) {
        var gaProducts = [];
        for(var i=0 ; i<prdList.length ; i++) {
            gaProducts.push({id:prdList[i].id, name:prdList[i].name, price:Number(prdList[i].price), brand:prdList[i].brand, category:gaCategory, variant: '', quantity:Number(prdList[i].quantity)});
        }
        return gaProducts;
    }
    
    //바로구매 버튼 클릭 시
    function pushGADetail() {
        var gaId = '354069935';
        var gaName = $('.prod_title p').text();
        var gaPrice = isNaN($('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val()) ? 0 : $('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val();
        var gaBrand = $('#hdelvMafcEntrNm').text();
        var gaQuantity = $('#inpOrderQty').val();
        var prdList;
        var gaProducts = [];
        var gaPrdInfo = {id : gaId, name : gaName, price : gaPrice, brand : gaBrand, quantity : gaQuantity};
        
        prdList = getPrdList(arguments, gaPrdInfo);
        gaProducts = getPrdListToJson(prdList);
        
        dataLayer.push({
            'event' : 'select',
            'ecommerce' : {
                'select' : {
                    'products'  : gaProducts
                }
            }
        });
        
    }
    
    //북카트담기 버튼 클릭 시
    function pushGAAddToCart() {
        var gaId = '354069935';
        var gaName = $('.prod_title p').text();
        var gaPrice = isNaN($('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val()) ? 0 : $('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val();
        var gaBrand = $('#hdelvMafcEntrNm').text();
        var gaQuantity = $('#inpOrderQty').val();
        var prdList;
        var gaProducts = [];
        var gaPrdInfo = {id : gaId, name : gaName, price : gaPrice, brand : gaBrand, quantity : gaQuantity};
        
        prdList = getPrdList(arguments, gaPrdInfo);
        gaProducts = getPrdListToJson(prdList);
        
        dataLayer.push({
            'event' : 'addToCart',
            'ecommerce' : {
                'currencyCode': 'KRW',
                'add' : {
                    'products'  : gaProducts
                }
            }
        });
        
    }
    
    //상품페이지 로드 후
    $(function() {
    	var fancyFlag = "false";
    	var gaId = '354069935';
        var gaName = $('.prod_title p').text();
        var gaBrand = $('#hdelvMafcEntrNm').text();
        var gaPrice = 0;
        var gaQuantity = 1;
        var gaProducts = [];
        
        if(fancyFlag == "true") {
        	var price = $('.discountPrice').children('.price').text().replace(/,/gi,'');
            gaPrice = isNaN(price) ? 0 : price;
        } else {
            gaPrice = isNaN($('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val()) ? 0 : $('#DISPOINT_SALE_UNITCOST').val();
        }
        
        gaProducts.push({id : gaId, name : gaName, price : gaPrice, brand : gaBrand, category: gaCategory, quantity : gaQuantity, variant:''});
        
        dataLayer.push({
            'event' : 'detail',
            'ecommerce' : {
                'detail' : {
                    'products'  : gaProducts
                }
            }
        });
    });
    
</script>

    function fn_addCartList_relProduct(formObj, checkBoxNm) {
        var checkedCnt = $(':checkbox[name="'+checkBoxNm+'"]:checked').length;
        if(checkedCnt >= 0) {
            if(checkedCnt == 0) {
                addCartList(formObj, checkBoxNm); // 0건일때는 공통메소드에서 처리
            } else if(checkedCnt > 0) {
                if(confirm("총 "+checkedCnt+"개의 상품을 북카트에 담으시겠습니까?")) {
                    addCartList(formObj, checkBoxNm); // 북카트 담기
                    $(':checkbox[name="'+checkBoxNm+'"]:checked').attr("checked", ""); // 성공유무와 상관없이 초기화
                }
            }
        }
    }

            url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=BestsellerHourNew201605&bestTp="+bestTp+"&dispNo="+dispNo+"&searchDay="+searchParam+"&clickCnb=Y";

            url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=BestsellerHourNew201605&bestTp="+bestTp+"&dispNo="+dispNo;
        }
        
        if(dateDiv == "1"){
                document.location.href = url;
        }else if(dateDiv == "2"){
            clttp="01";
            if(searchYn == "Y"){
                goBestWeek("27", searchParam, dispNo);
            }else{
                
                goBestWeek("01");
            }
        }else if(dateDiv == "3"){
            clttp="81";
            if(searchYn == "Y"){
                goBestMonth("28", searchParam, dispNo);
            }else{
                goBestMonth("81");
            }
        }else if(dateDiv == "4"){
            clttp="82";
            if(searchYn == "Y"){
                goBestYear("82", searchParam, dispNo);
            }else{
                goBestYear("82");
            }   
        }

        
        return false;
    });

    function setCate1Depth (){
        if ($('.book').hasClass("on")){
            cate1DepthDiv = '1';
        }else if ($('.book').hasClass("on")){
            
        }
    }
    
    function removeClassFn(maxCnt,currNum, idNm,classNm){
        var cnt = maxCnt+1;
        for(i = 1 ; i < cnt ; i++){
            if(i!=currNum){
                $(idNm+i).removeClass(classNm);
            }
        }        
    }

    // 상단탭, - 당일(1), 주간(2), 월간(3), 연간(4) 정리 
    function cateTab(num){
        //탭 클릭시 페이징을  1로 셋팅     
        comPageNum = 1;
        $('#cateTabId'+num).addClass("current");
        removeClassFn(4,num,'#cateTabId','current');
        //현재 상단 탭 셋팅 (당일, 주간, 월간)
        dateDiv = num ; 
        if(num == 1){
            clttp="01";
            goBestToday("01");
        }else if(num == 2){
        // 주간
            clttp="01";
            goBestWeek("01");
        }else if(num == 3){
        // 월간
            clttp="81";
            goBestMonth("81");
        }else if(num == 4){
        // 연간
            clttp="82";
            goBestYear("82");
        }
    }

    //당일 순위 메인 10개 ajax, 주간 이전순위 보기
    function goBestToday(clttp) {
        var url="";     
        if(bestTp == "1"){          
            url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=BestsellerHourNew201605&bestTp="+bestTp+"&dispNo="+dispNo;
        }else{
            url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=BestsellerHourNew201605&bestTp="+bestTp+"&dispNo="+dispNo+"&clickCnb=Y";
        }
        document.location.href = url; 
    }

    //주간 순위 메인 10개 ajax, 주간 이전순위 보기
    function goBestWeek(cltTp, sDate, cate) {
    
        if(cate == "weekSch"){
            page:comPageNum = "1";
            cate = "week";
        }
        if(cate == "week"){
            clickCnb = "Y";
            searchYn = "Y";
            searchParam = sDate;
            searchCate = cate;
        }
        var url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=BestsellerHourNewWeekList201605_xml";        
        $.ajax({
            url: url,
            type: 'POST',
            contentType: 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8', 
            data: {
                cltTp:cltTp,
                cltWeek:sDate,
                category:cate,
                bestTp:bestTp,
                dispNo:dispNo,
                clickCnb:clickCnb,
                page:comPageNum             
            },
            success: function(jdata){
                jdata = eval("{"+jdata+"}");
                if(jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K == null || jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K == ""){goNullData();return;}                
                // 랭킹 히스토리 셀릭트 박스 만들어주기
                setTopHistoryList(jdata.returnObj.cltWeek, jdata.returnObj.selectCond, jdata.returnObj.selectDate);
                // 리스트 만들어 주기
                goListView(jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K, "week", jdata.returnObj.jDispNo, jdata.returnObj.iconList, jdata.returnObj.iconListForPresent, jdata.returnObj.priceList, jdata.returnObj.starPointList, jdata.returnObj.eventList);
                // 페이징 만들어 주기   
                printProductListPageNavi(jdata.returnObj.totalCnt, cltTp, "week");
                
            },
            error: function(data, status, err) {
            }
        });
    }

    function goNullData(){
        var list = "";
        var divList = "";
        divList = $(".rankBestContentList");
        divList.empty();

        list = "<ol><li>조회된 랭킹 리스트가 없습니다.</li></ol>";
        divList.append($(list));
    }
    //월간 순위 메인 10개 ajax
    function goBestMonth(cltTp, sDate, cate) {
        if(cate == "monthSch"){
            page:comPageNum = "1";
            cate = "month";
        }
        if(cate == "month"){
            clickCnb = "Y";
            searchYn = "Y";
            searchParam = sDate;
            searchCate = cate;
        }   
        var url = "/display/collectlist.do?_method=bestsellerHourNewMonthList201605_xml";     
        $.ajax({
            url: url,
            type: 'POST',
            contentType: 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8', 
            data: {
                cltTp:cltTp,
                cltWeek:sDate,
                category:cate,
                bestTp:bestTp,
                dispNo:dispNo,
                clickCnb:clickCnb,
                page:comPageNum
            },
            success: function(jdata){
                jdata = eval("{"+jdata+"}");
                if(jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K == null || jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K == ""){goNullData();return;}
                // 랭킹 히스토리 셀릭트 박스 만들어주기
                setTopHistoryList(jdata.returnObj.cltWeek, jdata.returnObj.selectCond, jdata.returnObj.selectDate);
                // 리스트 만들어 주기
                goListView(jdata.returnObj.BOOK_K, "month",  jdata.returnObj.jDispNo, jdata.returnObj.iconList, jdata.returnObj.iconListForPresent, jdata.returnObj.priceList, jdata.returnObj.starPointList, jdata.returnObj.eventList);
                // 페이징 만들어 주기   
                printProductListPageNavi(jdata.returnObj.totalCnt, cltTp, "month");
            },
            error: function(data, status, err) {
            }
        });
    }

    function directOrd(prdNo) {
        var frm = document.Goods;    
        frm.action = "https://book.interpark.com/order/tmpordlist.do?useSSL=YES";
        frm["_method"].value="saveDirectTempOrder";
        frm.DIR_PRD_QTY.value = 1;
        frm.CART_PRD_NO_0.value = 1;
        frm.DIR_PRD_NO.value = prdNo;
        frm.CART_PRD_NO_0.value = prdNo;
        //frm.sc.prdNo.value = prdNo;
        frm.target = "";
        frm.submit();            
    }

    //페이징
    function goPaging(pageNum, cltTp, gubun) {
        comPageNum = pageNum;
        if(gubun == "year"){
            goBestYear(cltTp, searchParam, searchCate);
        }else if(gubun == "month"){
            goBestMonth(cltTp, searchParam, searchCate);
        }else if(gubun == "week"){
            goBestWeek(cltTp, searchParam, searchCate);         
        }
        $('html, body').animate({scrollTop:0}, 'fast');
    }

    //랭킹 리스트 만들어 주는 펑션
    function goListView(obj, gbn, dispNo, iconList, iconListForPresent, priceList, starPointList, eventList){
        var ebPrdNo="";

        var setPrdStr = "singleType";

        // 무조건 주간 랭킹으로 연결 되게 
        if("028998" == dispNo||"028997" == dispNo||"028996" == dispNo||"028995" == dispNo||"028994" == dispNo||"028993" == dispNo||"028992" == dispNo) {
            setPrdStr = "setType";
        } 
        
        if(obj.length > 0) {
            var cls = "";           
            var list = "";
            var divList = "";
            divList = $(".rankBestContentList");
            divList.empty();
            list = "<ol>";
            var prdIdxStr = "";
            
            for(var i = 0; i <obj.length ; i++){
                // 판매량 부분은 삭제됨 201605 개편 사항 작업자 : 김범래 (엑션에서는 잇음)
                if(obj[i].listImg.indexOf("h.")>-1){
                    var tempImgStr1= "";
                    var tempImgStr2= "";
                    tempImgStr1=obj[i].listImg.split("h.");
                    tempImgStr2= tempImgStr1[0] + "s." +tempImgStr1[1];
                }else{
                    tempImgStr2= obj[i].listImg;
                }
            
                if(priceList.length > 0){
                    for(var j = 0; j <priceList.length ; j++){
                        if(obj[i].prdNo ==priceList[j].prdNo){
                            if ("Y" == priceList[j].setPrdYn) {
                                setPrdStr = "setType";
                            } else {
                                setPrdStr = "singleType";
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                    
                var rowValue = i+1;
                list +="   <li>";
                list +="   <div class='listItem "+setPrdStr+"'>";
                list +="       <div class='cover'>";
                list +="           <div class='coverImage'>";
                list +="               <label>";
                list +="                <a href='"+obj[i].linkUrl+"&sc.saNo="+ saNoList[saIndex] +"'  target='_blank'>";
                list +="                   <span class='checkBox'>";
                list +="                       <input type='checkbox' name='_KEY' value='"+obj[i].prdNo+"'>";
                list +="                   </span>";
                list +="                   <img src='"+tempImgStr2+"' alt='"+obj[i].prdNm.replace("(양장)","")+"'>";
                list +="                   <i class='decoFront'></i>";
                list +="                </a>";
                list +="               </label>";
                list +="           </div>";
                list +="           <div class='coverOption'>";
                list +="               <ul>";
                list +="                   <li class='cart'>";
                list +="                       <a href='#' value='"+obj[i].prdNo+"'class='cartGo'><span>CART</span></a>";
                list +="                   </li>";
                list +="                   <li class='buy'>";
                list +="                       <a href='javascript:directOrd("+obj[i].prdNo+");'><span>BUY</span></a>";
                list +="                   </li>";
                list +="               </ul>";
                list +="           </div>";
                list +="           <div class='rankNumber digit2'>";
                list +=             obj[i].dispPrir; //  랭킹 순위가 태그로 나옴 주의 퍼블에게 미리 요청해야함   예시)  일단위 <span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_B01 "></span>   씹단위 <span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_M09 "></span><span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_M09 "></span> 백단위 :     <span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_S01 "></span><span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_S00 "></span><span class="rankBtn_ctrl rkNum_S00 "></span>
                list +="           </div>";
                list +="       </div>";
                list +="       <div class='itemIcon'>";
                if(iconList.length > 0){
                    for(var j = 0; j <iconList.length ; j++){
                        if(obj[i].prdNo == iconList[j].prdNo){
                            if( iconList[j].cltIcn.indexOf('01') > -1){
                                // 베스트
                                list +="    <span class='bestSeller'>베스트셀러</span>";
                            }
                            if( iconList[j].icnTp.indexOf('07') > -1){
                                // 인터파크 추천
                                list +="    <span class='interparkRecommend'>인터파크추천</span>";
                            }
                            if( iconList[j].cltIcn.indexOf('03') > -1){
                                // 스테디셀러
                                list +="    <span class='steadySeller'>스테디셀러</span>";
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                if(iconListForPresent.length > 0){
                    for(var j = 0; j <iconListForPresent.length ; j++){
                        if(obj[i].prdNo == iconListForPresent[j].prdNo){
                            if( iconListForPresent[j].presentYn.indexOf('Y') > -1){
                                // 베스트
                         //       list +="           <span class='gift'>사은품</span>"; // 추후 적용
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                list +="       </div>";
                list +="       <a href='"+obj[i].linkUrl+"&sc.saNo="+ saNoList[saIndex] +"' target='_blank'>";
                list +="           <div class='itemName'>";
                list +="               <strong>"+obj[i].prdNm.replace("(양장)","")+"</strong>";
                list +="           </div>";
                list +="           <div class='itemMeta'>";
                var editorNm = "";
                if(obj[i].editorNm != ""){
                    editorNm = ": "+obj[i].editorNm;
                }
                list +="               <span class='author'>"+obj[i].author.substr(0, 70)+editorNm+"</span>";
                list +="               <span class='company'>"+obj[i].hdelvMafcEntrNm+"</span>";
                list +="           </div>";
                // 가격 설정
                //판매지수는 가격에서 쿼리함.
                prdIdxStr = "";
                if(priceList.length > 0){
                    for(var j = 0; j <priceList.length ; j++){
                        if(obj[i].prdNo ==priceList[j].prdNo){
                            var dcRtPer =""; 
                            dcRtPer = priceList[j].dcRtPer;
                            var blcPointDcRtPer = "";
                            blcPointDcRtPer = priceList[j].blcPointDcRtPer;
                            list +="           <div class='priceWrap'>";
                            list +="               <span class='price'>";
                            list +="                   <em>"+priceList[j].saleUnitcost+"</em>";
                            list +="                   <span class='currency'>원</span>";
                            list +="               </span>";
                            if(dcRtPer!=null||blcPointDcRtPer!=null||dcRtPer!=""||blcPointDcRtPer!=""){
                                list +="               <span class='benefits'> ";
                                list +="                   <span>(</span>";
                                if(dcRtPer!=null&&dcRtPer!=""){
                                    list +="                   <span class='discount'>";
                                    list +="                       <em>"+dcRtPer+"</em>";
                                    list +="                       <span class='unit'>할인</span>";
                                    list +="                   </span>";
                                }
                                if(blcPointDcRtPer!=null&&blcPointDcRtPer!=""){
                                list +="                   <span class='save'>";
                                list +="                       <em>"+blcPointDcRtPer+"</em>";
                                list +="                       <span class='unit'>적립</span>";
                                list +="                   </span>";
                                }
                                list +="                   <span>)</span>";
                                list +="               </span>";
                            }
                            list +="           </div>";

                            // 판매지수 추가 2017.1.16 
                            var prdIdxVal = priceList[j].prdIdxVal;  //StringUtils.defaultString(dto.getPrdIdxVal(), "0")   ;
                            //alert(prdIdxVal);
                            
                            if(prdIdxVal == null || "null" ==  prdIdxVal || "0" ==prdIdxVal || "" ==prdIdxVal ) {
                                prdIdxVal = "-";
                            }else{
                                prdIdxVal = fnCommas(prdIdxVal); //gate/js/common.js
                            }
                            if("[330075799, 330075897, 330075900, 330075901, 330075903, 330075905, 330075908, 330075909, 330075911, 330076144, 283903874, 283903875, 283903876, 283903877, 314035386, 314038074, 314039472, 314040753, 314041736, 314042485, 314043736, 314044436, 314045354, 316241312, 316241849, 316243129, 316244661, 316245317, 316245619, 316246575, 316246999, 316247879, 316248460, 334275776, 334275844, 334275845, 334275846, 334275847, 334275892, 334275894, 334275895, 334275898, 334275902, 334275910, 334275912, 339126309, 339126317, 339126355, 339126388, 339126357, 339126392, 339126386, 339126394, 344575863, 344576106, 344576117, 344576121, 344576122, 344576126, 344576127, 344576129, 348752393, 348752808, 348753008, 348753013, 348753015, 348753018, 348753019, 348753209, 348753212, 348753217, 348753220, 348753221, 348753225, 352180193, 352180401, 352180403, 352180405, 352180409, 352180411, 352180414, 352180415, 352180422, 352180423, 352180424, 352180427, 352180431, 352180432, 352230522]".indexOf(priceList[j].prdNo) == -1) {                                
								prdIdxStr +="       <div class='saleIndex'>";
								prdIdxStr +="       <span class='title'>판매지수</span>";
								prdIdxStr +="       <em class='indexNumber'>"+prdIdxVal+ "</em>";
								prdIdxStr +="       </div>";
							}
                        }
                    }
                }
                
                list +="       </a>";

                if(starPointList.length > 0){

                            list +="               <span class='starRate' style='width:"+starPoint10+"%'>"+starPoint+"</span>";

                                }

                                list +="               </li>";
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    list +="           </ul>";
                    list +="       </div>";

                list +="   </div>";
                list +="</li>";
            }
            list +="</ol>";
            divList.append($(list));
            // 페이지가 로드된 이후에 셀렉드 박스 숨기기
            $('#filterPeriodId').removeClass('on');
        }
    }
        
    // 랭킹 히스토리 셀릭트 박스 만들어주기
    function setTopHistoryList(cltWeek, selectCond, selectDate){
        bestFrm.cltWeek.value = cltWeek;    
        //기준일 밀어 넣기
        $('#periodStandardDate').html(selectCond);
        if(cltWeek != "" ){
            $(".periodSelector").empty();
            $('.periodSelector').html(selectDate);
        }
    }
    
    function printProductListPageNavi(totalCnt, cltTp, gubun) {
        
        //$('.rankBestPagination').hide();
        pageDiv =""; 
        pageDiv +="<a href='#' class='arrow first'  id='prd_navi_first_span'><span>처음</span></a>";
        pageDiv +=" <a href='#' class='arrow prev'  id='prd_navi_before_span'><span>이전</span></a> ";
        pageDiv +=" <span class='numList'> ";
        pageDiv +=" </span> ";
        pageDiv +=" <a href='#' class='arrow next' id='prd_navi_after_span'><span>다음</span></a> ";
        pageDiv +=" <a href='#' class='arrow last' id='prd_navi_last_span'><span>마지막</span></a> ";
                    
        $('.rankBestPagination').html(pageDiv); 
        
        comTotalCnt = totalCnt;
        totalPage = Math.ceil(comTotalCnt/comRow);
        
        var naviStr = "";

        startPageIndex = 0; //시작 Page Index 초기화
        endPageIndex = 0;   //끝   Page Index 초기화
        
        if(comPageNum < startPageIndex || comPageNum > endPageIndex) {
            var pageIndex = Math.ceil(comPageNum/pageCount);
            
            endPageIndex = pageCount * pageIndex;
            startPageIndex = endPageIndex -  (pageCount-1);
            
            if(totalPage < endPageIndex){
                endPageIndex = totalPage;
            }
        }
        
        for(var i=startPageIndex; i<=endPageIndex; i++) {
            var cls = "";
            if(comPageNum == i){
                cls = " class='current'";
            }
            naviStr += "<a href='javascript:goPaging(" + i + ",\""+cltTp+"\",\""+gubun+"\");' "+cls+">" + i + "</a>";            
        }
        
        $('.numList').html(naviStr);

        var firstOnClickEvent = "";
        if(1 < comPageNum) {
            firstOnClickEvent = "onClick='javascript:goPaging(1, \""+cltTp+"\",\""+gubun+"\");'";
        }
        document.getElementById("prd_navi_first_span").innerHTML = "<span "+firstOnClickEvent+">처음</span>";

        var beforeOnClickEvent = "";
        cursor = "";
        if(startPageIndex > pageCount) {
            beforeOnClickEvent = "onClick='javascript:goPaging("+Number(startPageIndex-pageCount)+", \""+cltTp+"\", \""+gubun+"\");'";
        }
        document.getElementById("prd_navi_before_span").innerHTML = "<span "+beforeOnClickEvent+">이전</span>";
        
        var afterOnClickEvent = "";
        cursor = "";
        if(Number(endPageIndex*comRow) < comTotalCnt) {
            afterOnClickEvent = "onClick='javascript:goPaging("+Number(endPageIndex+1)+", \""+cltTp+"\", \""+gubun+"\");'";
        }
        document.getElementById("prd_navi_after_span").innerHTML = "<span "+afterOnClickEvent+">다음</span>";

        var lastOnClickEvent = "";
        cursor = "";
        if(1<totalPage && comPageNum!=totalPage) {
            lastOnClickEvent = "onClick='javascript:goPaging("+totalPage+", \""+cltTp+"\", \""+gubun+"\");'";
        }
        document.getElementById("prd_navi_last_span").innerHTML = "<span "+lastOnClickEvent+">마지막</span>";
    }
</script>

lines=[]
for index, li in enumerate(lis):
    rank = li.select('.rankNumber.digit2>span')
    if len(rank)>1:
        rank_1= rank[0]['class'][1].split('_')[1].split('0')[1]
        rank_2=rank[1]['class'][1].split('_')[1].split()[0][-1]
        rank = rank_1+rank_2
    else:   
        rank = rank[0]['class']
        rank[0].split("_")
        rank = li.select_one('.rankNumber.digit2').find('span')['class']
        rank[0].split("_")
        rank = rank[1].split("_")
        rank = rank[1]
        rank = rank.split('0')
        rank = rank[1]


    bookname = li.select_one('.itemName').string
    name = li.select_one('.author').string
    publisher = li.select_one('.company').string
    price = li.select_one('.price').get_text().strip().split()
    price = price[0].split(',')
    price = ''.join(price)
    int(price)
    href = li.find('a')['href']

    sub_url = site + href
    sub_req = requests.get(sub_url)
    sub_html = sub_req.text
    sub_soup = BeautifulSoup(sub_html, 'html.parser')
    published_date = sub_soup.select('.bInfo_txt>li')[-3].string
    number_of_pages = sub_soup.select('.bInfo_txt>li')[-2].string
    number_of_pages = number_of_pages.split()
    number_of_pages = number_of_pages[2]
    number_of_pages = int(number_of_pages)
    
    lines.append([rank,bookname,name,publisher,price,published_date,number_of_pages])
